  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the effect of an experimental toothpaste on
      maintaining gingival health over a 24 week period measured through modified gingival index,
      bleeding, plaque, and plaque bacteria. Prior to commencing study treatment, subjects will
      undergo a dental prophylaxis followed by a 2 week period of oral hygiene instruction and
      weekly professional tooth cleaning to bring the subjects to their optimum gingival health
      prior to commencing study treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
